Jacques Andre Zakari Lambo (amụrụ ya na 14 Mee 1976 na Argoum Doutchi) bụ onye bọọlụ bọọlụ Naijiria, onye na-agba bọọlụ dị ka onye na-aga n'ihu.
Ọ gbara ọtụtụ ndu ọkachamara ya na Poland na Belgium, na-apụta maka klọb iri dị iche iche.
Lambo malitere ọrụ ọkachamara ya na otu egwuregwu Naijiria JS du Ténéré; mgbe ahụ ọ gbara bọọlụ maka klọb Burkinabé Etoile Filante Ouagadougou
Ọ bịarutere Kraków mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na asatọ, n'oge na-adịghịkwa anya ọ ghọrọ onye na-agba bọọlụ na Hutnik Kraków
Mgbe ọ nọrọ obere oge na Spanish RCD Mallorca, ọ gara Belgium, mgbe ọ nọrọ ọtụtụ n'ime afọ ndị sochirinụ, na-egwu maka Eendracht Aalst, UR Namur, R.F.C
Tournai, KVC Zwevegem Sport, KVK Ieper na Eendracht Wervik
Ọ gbakwara bọọlụ maka VfR Mannheim German na nke ugboro abụọ, maka Hutnik Kraków.
Zakari Lambo nọchitere anya Niger na ọkwa dị elu, na-agba goolu iri na ise na egwuregwu iri abụọ.
Lambo bụ nna onye na-agba bọọlụ Zakari Junior Lambo, ọ na-agbara ndị otu mba Niger Bọọlụ
